get="#pmb11740">Hofmannsthal, Hugo von</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01160">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 11.  8. 1901</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCollection" target="L01162">Schnitzler an Beer-Hofmann, 17. 8. 1901</ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01159">Schnitzler an Hofmannsthal, 10. 8. 1901</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="L01163">Hofmannsthal an Schnitzler, 19. 8. 1901</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
